TravelPackage.Title: New York City
TravelPackage.Description: New York City is a vibrant global metropolis known for its iconic skyline, cultural diversity, and nonstop energy.
TravelPackage.DetailedDescription: Home to landmarks like Times Square, Central Park, and the Statue of Liberty, NYC blends history with innovation. Its five boroughs pulse with art, finance, fashion, and food, making it a magnet for dreamers and doers worldwide.

TravelPackage.Description: Rome is a living museum of ancient wonders and culinary indulgence.
TravelPackage.DetailedDescription: Marvel at the Colosseum, Pantheon, and Trevi Fountain as history surrounds you. Savor pasta and gelato while wandering through centuries-old streets

TravelPackage.Title: London
TravelPackage.Description: London fuses royal heritage with modern vibrancy across its iconic skyline.
TravelPackage.DetailedDescription: Big Ben, Buckingham Palace, and the London Eye anchor its historic core. Red buses and the Thames weave through a city of culture and innovation
